design (https://www.slideshare.net/sudhirpg/ganglia-monitoring-tool)
------
1. Monitors clusters and grids
2. Used multicast listen/announce protocol
3. Has one web client connected to a central server agent 
4. Central agent is connected to invidual nodes in the cluster to collect metrics
5. Any node in the client cluster can failover to perform as a server node
6. Used heartbeats and polling to check the health status